Class DocumentDelegate

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.nikhef.xhtmlrenderer.swing.DocumentDelegate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Document, Node
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TemplateDocument
    public class DocumentDelegate
extends Object
implements Document
    Document class that delegates all methods to another Document.

    • Method Detail

      • isValid

        public boolean isValid()
        returns whether this delegate has a valid document, or if it is null.

        When this method returns false, one should not call any other method before running setDocument(org.w3c.dom.Document).
